address.streetAddress: Tourmaline Plan, Seasons at Park Circle

location.fullValue: Tourmaline Plan, Seasons at Park Circle

data.description: Welcome to Trailside by Beazer Homes at Park Circle. This beautiful floorplan offers just over 2,732 sq. ft. with 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a 3-car garage. A cozy open floor plan of the Great Room, Dining Space, and Kitchen. The bedroom on the main level has an adjacent bathroom with a walk-in shower. Perfect private space for your guests and family. Lots of cabinetry and storage with a large island. Arrive upstairs to 3 Bedrooms. Bedrooms 2 and 3 share a bathroom with double sinks. Lots of room in the upstairs Laundry Room with natural light. The Primary Bedroom is spacious, with many windows and tons of room in the walk-in. The community has a workout center, community center a BBQ frill, Courts, a park, loads of trails, and dog parks all within walking distance. There are great schools to choose from, local farmers markets, and food truck Fridays!
